# Phase 18 verdict: central half-pixel correction

## Executive recommendation

| Item | Verdict |
|------|---------|
| **Site** | `Direct3d11_StateCache.cpp:setViewport` ‚Äî fold into c9 `viewportData[2]` and `viewportData[3]` (`.z`/`.w`) |
| **Sign** | **`z += +1/width`**, **`w -= +1/height`** (equivalently add `+1/width` to the third component, subtract `+1/height` from the fourth) |
| **Magnitude** | Exactly **`1.0f/width`** and **`1.0f/height`** in NDC offset space ‚Äî not `0.5/width` |
| **Mechanism** | **Primary: global XYZRHW position convention mismatch** (D3D9 rasterizer `-0.5` rule + baked `ms_pixelOffset=-0.5` vs D3D11 center-sampling). **Secondary visibility factor: split-texture join at screen center** ‚Äî not an alternate root cause |
| **Dead stub** | **`getOneToOneUVMapping` is irrelevant** ‚Äî leave it fatal |

